fields.title: Celestial Ring Set
fields.description: A pair of stacking rings, symbolizing the sun and moon. Hand-hammered for a subtle shine that catches the light beautifully.

fields.title: Handmade Beaded Stone Bracelet
fields.description: Crafted by hand with natural stones and polished glass beads, this bracelet brings together earthy texture and timeless charm. Each piece is uniquely strung for balance and color harmony — perfect for everyday wear or as a meaningful gift.

fields.title: Minimal Gemstone Gold Rings
fields.description: 14k Gold - Elegant and understated, these minimalist gold rings feature a single hand-set gemstone for a subtle touch of color and shine. Perfect for stacking or wearing solo, each piece highlights timeless design and refined craftsmanship.

fields.title: Variety Gold Earrings
fields.description: A curated collection of handcrafted gold earrings featuring hoops, studs, and drops — each designed to suit any mood or occasion. Made with high-quality gold vermeil and polished to a radiant shine, these pieces add effortless elegance to every look.

fields.title: Custom Jewelry Order
fields.description: Design your dream piece with our custom jewelry service — from sketch to final polish. Choose your metals, gemstones, and style, and we’ll handcraft a one-of-a-kind creation that reflects your story and personal style.

fields.title: Thin Gold Bracelets
fields.description: Delicate yet radiant, these thin gold bracelets are designed for effortless elegance. Available in both chain and bangle styles, each piece is handcrafted to layer beautifully or shine on its own — a timeless staple for everyday wear.

fields.title: Pajama Labubu Clothes
fields.description: Adorably cozy and perfectly fitted, these handmade pajama sets keep your Labubu snug in style. Featuring soft fabrics, playful patterns, and tiny finishing touches, they’re ideal for bedtime displays or photo-ready cuteness.

fields.title: Floral Dress Sets
fields.description: A matching set of handcrafted dresses made just for Labubu, featuring delicate stitching, soft fabrics, and whimsical details that bring each character’s personality to life. Perfect for display or photos, these custom outfits add a touch of charm and individuality to your collectible duo.

fields.title: Crotchet Snow White Dress
fields.description: This handmade crochet dress captures Snow White’s classic charm with vibrant yarn, fine detailing, and a perfect miniature fit for your Labubu or collectible doll. Soft, durable, and irresistibly cute — it’s a fairytale outfit made for display or play.

fields.title: Custom Outfit Creation
fields.description: Bring your vision to life with a one-of-a-kind handmade outfit tailored for your Labubu or collectible doll. From concept to final stitch, each piece is designed to match your chosen theme, colors, and style — making every creation uniquely yours.

fields.title: Strawberry Rose Sugar Scrub
fields.description: A sweet, floral blend of crushed rose petals and ripe strawberry essence whipped into a soft sugar base. This exfoliating scrub gently polishes the skin while leaving it smooth, hydrated, and lightly scented with notes of fresh berries and blooms.

fields.title: Floral Bath Bombs
fields.description: Handmade with care, these bath bombs combine skin-softening oils, natural botanicals, and dried flower petals for a luxurious soak. Each bomb fizzes beautifully, releasing soothing aromas and nourishing ingredients that leave your skin silky smooth and your senses relaxed. Set of 3.

fields.title: Mini Fragrance Bottle Collection
fields.description: A charming assortment of handmade perfumes presented in custom mini glass bottles — perfect for gifting, travel, or trying new scents. Each fragrance is blended with essential oils and natural botanicals, offering a variety of notes from floral and citrus to warm amber and musk.

fields.title: Custom Soap Bars
fields.description: Create your perfect soap with our custom-made bars, handcrafted in small batches using nourishing oils, clays, and botanicals. Choose your scent, color, and design — from calming lavender to energizing citrus — for a personalized touch to your daily self-care ritual.

fields.title: Curated Bath Essentials Gift Set
fields.description: A beautifully curated collection of handmade bath essentials designed to pamper and relax. Each set includes a mix of soaps, bath bombs, scrubs, and candles — all crafted with natural ingredients, essential oils, and floral accents for a luxurious self-care experience. Perfect for birthdays, holidays, or “just because” moments.

fields.title: Soy Wax Candles
fields.description: Hand-poured from 100% natural soy wax, this candle offers a clean, long-lasting burn with a soft, soothing fragrance. Each one is crafted in small batches with cotton wicks and essential oils, creating a cozy atmosphere perfect for unwinding at home.

fields.title: Handmade Fragrance Oils
fields.description: Crafted in small batches, these handmade fragrances blend natural essential oils and botanical extracts for scents that are both unique and timeless. Each perfume is carefully balanced to highlight rich layers of floral, citrus, or woodsy notes — perfect for everyday wear or special occasions. Set of 4.

fields.title: Natural Bath Salts 3.5oz
fields.description: This bath salt is made with detoxifying sea salt and Epsom salts naturally soothe sore muscles and helps detoxify the body. Scented with essential oils and mixed with dried flowers, everything works together to create a seriously relaxing bath.

fields.title: Gold Flower Hair Pin
fields.description: Add a touch of delicate charm to your hairstyle with these handcrafted floral hair pins. Each pin features petite, detailed flowers paired with luminous pearls, creating timeless look. This pins are available in gold, silver, and rose gold finishes.

fields.title: Gemstone Glass Polyhedral Dice
fields.description: Gemstone Dichroic Glass Elven Cut Polyhedral Dice (With Box) DnD Full Set. Each set of gemstone/resin dice is unique in color, pattern, and translucency, and may differ from the product picture. Dice made from gemstone can be fragile, so we recommend you avoid rolling them on hard surfaces.

fields.title: Love Bunny Dice
fields.description: Elevate your gaming experience with these enchanting handcrafted bunny-themed dice! Each polyhedral die is meticulously crafted from crystal-clear epoxy resin, featuring adorable bunny stickers 🐰 suspended within. The magical liquid core creates a whimsical floating effect as the dice roll across your table.

fields.title: Natural Rose Quartz Dice Set
fields.description: All of our elements and symbols are inspired by vintage image. The gemstone are picked up from nature before shaping into geometric dice. They are not perfect, but unique. When you look at them closely, each of them is shining of natural power.

fields.title: Aurora's Tears Dice Set
fields.description:
"Shards of Starlight"
Legends whisper that when the northern lights weep, their tears crystalize into shimmering shards that mortals may hold. Aurora’s Tears captures that ethereal beauty in every sharp edge—glimmering hues that shift and dance like starlight on ice. Each roll feels like summoning the skies themselves, a reminder that magic is never far from reach.

fields.title: Amethyst DnD Dice Set
fields.description: To roll or to wear. To your, my dear loved one. Amethyst can increase your intuition. You can wear this as a pendant while your roll them on the table top. To heal or to have fun. Both rights are on your hands. To protect you, to be firm at any occasion. You have this stable energy inside out. You have strong believes, hard as the gemstone. Roll them or wear them spiritually and confidently.

fields.title: Miss Darling Mahjong Tile Set
fields.description: Miss Darling is a Grandmillennial’s dream: designed for lovers of needlepoint, heirloom china, and garden party glam. Every one of our 160 tiles features a hand-drawn design for a truly unique look, engraved and hand-painted on a soft white face that fades into a Wedgwood blue ombré.

fields.title: Houseplant Mahjong Tile Set
fields.description: Introducing our one-of-a-kind Houseplant Mahjong Set! Every tile has been thoughtfully designed by hand—no AI, just original illustrations crafted with care by a real artist. Perfect for plant lovers and game enthusiasts alike, this unique set brings the charm of houseplants to the classic game of mahjong. Truly authentic and exclusive, you won’t find anything like it!

fields.title: Custom Wood Grain Guitar Capo
fields.description: Our Personalized Guitar Capo unlocks a new realm of musical expression. This capo not only enhances the tone of your guitar but also adds a personal touch, as it is engineered for both precision and durability.

fields.title: 17-Key Personalized Kalimba
fields.description: Discover the enchanting sound of the 17-Key Kalimba, also known as the African thumb piano. Handcrafted from quality wood and tuned for rich, melodic tones, this beautiful finger piano is the perfect gift for music lovers of all ages – from curious kids to creative adults.

fields.title: Custom Wooden Guitar Picks Box
fields.description: The color, texture, and wood grain of any natural wood product will vary from piece to piece, but this is what makes this guitar pick holder unique. Our pick case are crafted from high quality, sturdy wood. The edge treatment of the product is very meticulously smooth, and the box will keep your picks safe and protected.

fields.title: Engraved Wooden Ring Box
fields.description: Add a bit of class to your special events with this beautifully crafted wooden ring box, perfect for an engagement or wedding. For wedding photos, proposals, or any special occasion (anniversary, Valentine's Day, birthday), this laser-engraved hardwood ring box is the perfect keepsake.

fields.title: Engraved Wooden Watch for Men
fields.description: A one-of-a-kind and special gift for any man in your life. This laser engraved Wooden Watch with Gift Box is ideal for Husband, Boyfriend, Graduation, Junior Groomsmen, Father's Day, Birthdays, and many other occasions.

fields.title: Wooden Hip Flask and Cups Set
fields.description: For the most fashionable and hassle-free way to transport your favorite drink, we provide the Personalized Wooden Flask. This flask is hand-crafted from stainless steel with American Wood and is incredibly portable, making it ideal for camping, parties, sporting events, and travel. Put your own spin on it by adding your initials or full name. This long-lasting thermos is crafted from premium food-grade 304 stainless steel.
